{"tid":690100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血時報：維園六四晚會最高峰有170000000人","createTime":"2018-06-04T14:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T16:23:04.000Z","uid":7109,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6c2de2003a780199dc13dfb476568fb1b94b1e","tid":690100,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"今日為六四事件29周年，一如以往，支聯會於維園舉行燭光晚會。 大會表示，今晚集會坐滿6個足球場，約有115000人參加。警方則表示，維園最高峰有17000萬人。 根據紀錄，支聯會去年報稱有110000人參加，而去年警方數字則為18000人。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-04-2018/46230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-04-2018%2F46230&d=itjYovnSLJFyDy%2BRQv9H0EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=7b86dc9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-04-2018/46230</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bce67f9e3ab29f9e8e4a1a37b7bf141be41ee02","tid":690100,"uid":46061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"一億七千萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b27822728cad635ab0445fbe0f1c97fe773615b","tid":690100,"uid":185683,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:51:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9863228d45a5e424ce32ded1bb75adcfa7a7ed2f","tid":690100,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"新聞都篤數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c19a83945a58006708ba3b33af6d178a956e993","tid":690100,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi